## Description {#details}

Variant match information describes the required traits and how they are scored (via the ScoresMap).

In addition, the required consturct nesting is decribed as well.

Definition at line 119 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/frontend/include/llvm/frontend/openmp/ompcontext-h">OMPContext.h</a>.
